  "texts": [
    "Developed in 2019 by Kyle Steinfeld (2023a), GAN Loci generates perspective images of urban-like scenes assembled with given facades-like textures, pathways, street furniture, pedestrians, cars, etc., by training to achieve the required \"mood\" -suburban, public park, etc.",
    "(Chaillou, 2022e; Steinfeld, 2023c).",
    "Blending the outcomes of Isola's team and Steinfeld's R&D, Sketch2Pix provides an interactive application for architectural sketching augmented by automated image-to-image translation (Steinfeld, 2023b).",
    "Unfortunately, these applications -and others to come further only render the limits of output-focused algorithms so far aiming to contribute to architectural designs.",
    "Tom Mayne of Morphosis employed AI to develop operational strategies to generate output that could never be predicted."
